{"tid":591384,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[陪着我嘔吐物系列] 牛肉絲蘑菇通粉","createTime":"2018-03-13T13:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T13:20:41.000Z","uid":79353,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"713c2480cbf0aa38d938d6f523dde7ecc48183c7","tid":591384,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"繼爸爸食完我煮的嘔吐物烏冬之後，<br />\n而家到老母被處決 lol<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到煮出來咁大碟，部分俾我做早餐。仲收埋左成碟喺雪櫃俾媽媽聽日食，咁佢就唔洗煩午餐食乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">望着你講 也許更易<br />\n陪着我嘔這四個字</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日工作之後仲有精神喺廚房一路大大聲播歌一路煮簡單野食，真係好開心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/211703_53e0c3b3bab2f9b0aea14db84936163d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F211703_53e0c3b3bab2f9b0aea14db84936163d.jpg&h=b349af25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e7f280354f7d9962be85ae9b8ee896e385c6fb","tid":591384,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫牛肉絲咩"},{"pid":"c33898f9e934652e72f0a141679d98a061b66298","tid":591384,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"45e7f280354f7d9962be85ae9b8ee896e385c6fb","tid":591384,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫牛肉絲咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"惠康個包裝寫住牛肉絲，好似係 lol"},{"pid":"3b750054cc7f74275628a16109fdf91dca5aa58f","tid":591384,"uid":169108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:27:59.000Z"